<p>She, however, noted that the Federal Government is still working out practicalitiesÂ before the implementation of the new allowance for corps members.Â â€œThe financial implications have been worked out by the presidential committee that was set up and they have submitted their report to the President and the President has directed the report to us,â€ she said.</p><div class="0UaLArjh" style="clear:both;float:left;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9755093768544960"
